This file provides a template of display hierarchies for data encoded using the Parthenos Entities Model (rdfs v2.0). This model aims to cover the domain of research infrastructure information management practices and has as chief high level entities: Projects, Services, Datasets, Software and Actors. This template provides display ordering in the RDF Visualizer tool for these entities. This template also adopts wholesale additional property display hierarchies of CRM entities - of which the CRMpe model is an extension - that were originally made by the British Museum in the context of the ResearchSpace project.
